OL,3,CCampbell Hatton: 'My dad's death saved
OL,4,Cmy life'
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports Sports
OL,7,FCorrespondent Mike Hall spoke to
OL,8,FCampbell about his mental health after
OL,9,Fthe boxer chose to speak out to
OL,10,Fencourage others to seek help
OL,12,FThe son of the late world boxing
OL,13,Fchampion Ricky Hatton has revealed
OL,14,Fthat his dad's death is the reason he
OL,15,Fis alive today - admitting he was just
OL,16,F"weeks off" taking his own life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
