OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782314307
OL,3,CCampbell Hatton: 'My dad's death saved
OL,4,Cmy life'
OL,6,FIn an exclusive interview, the 25-year-
OL,7,Fold opened up about how his life was
OL,8,Fspiralling out of control with a
OL,9,Fsevere addiction to cocaine and
OL,10,Falcohol.
OL,12,FCampbell admitted his struggles began
OL,13,Fbefore his dad's death, noting he
OL,14,Ffound it incredibly difficult to walk
OL,15,Faway from his career in boxing,
OL,16,Falongside losing four close friends in
OL,17,Fa matter of months.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782314307
OL,3,CCampbell Hatton: 'My dad's death saved
OL,4,Cmy life'
OL,6,FHe says his dad's death in September
OL,7,F2025 "saved" his life because it
OL,8,Fforced him to address the way he was
OL,9,Ffeeling and go to rehab for his
OL,10,Faddiction.
OL,12,FCampbell, a dad-of-one, from Hyde,
OL,13,FTameside, says he has now turned his
OL,14,Flife around and plans a return to the
OL,15,Fboxing ring.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782314307
OL,3,CCampbell Hatton: 'My dad's death saved
OL,4,Cmy life'
OL,6,F"I've spent time in rehab and I was
OL,7,Fjust off the rails," he said. "There
OL,8,Fwas a six months where I lost four
OL,9,Fpeople who were really close to me.
OL,10,FEven before, I'd struggled to come to
OL,11,Fterms with retiring from boxing."
OL,13,FHe explained how his substance abuse
OL,14,Fquickly escalated as a coping mechanism
OL,16,F"Drinking was always part of that and
OL,17,FI was getting treatment for addiction
OL,18,Fwith cocaine as well. I think it all
OL,19,Fgoes hand-in-hand," he added.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782314307
OL,3,CCampbell Hatton: 'My dad's death saved
OL,4,Cmy life'
OL,6,F"I don't think anyone in rehab or
OL,7,Fstruggled with addiction - it is a
OL,8,Fpackage thing. I have the personality
OL,9,Fwhere it's all or nothing. Whether
OL,10,Fit's good or bad. It's just the way
OL,11,FI'm wired up."
OL,13,FCampbell openly admitted he tried to
OL,14,Ftake his own life a "couple of times"
OL,15,Fduring this dark period, and says he
OL,16,Fwas living "without any consequences"
OL,17,Fbecause he "wouldn't be around to deal
OL,18,Fwith it".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782314307
OL,3,CCampbell Hatton: 'My dad's death saved
OL,4,Cmy life'
OL,6,F"There was no thought to the future
OL,7,Fand it's a bit of miracle that I am
OL,8,Fstill here," he said.
OL,10,FThe dad revealed he was in such a bad
OL,11,Fplace in the weeks leading up to
OL,12,Flosing his father that his family
OL,13,Ffeared the worst when authorities
OL,14,Fapproached them.
OL,16,F"When the police were breaking the
OL,17,Fnews (of Ricky's death), a lot of my
OL,18,Ffamily thought it going to be about me
OL,19,F- and it probably were not far wrong.
OL,20,FIt was probably weeks off," he
OL,21,Frecalled.
OL,26,@yD@FpmyD@Wpn
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782314307
OL,3,CCampbell Hatton: 'My dad's death saved
OL,4,Cmy life'
OL,6,FHowever, he says the devastating loss
OL,7,Fof his father forced him to change his
OL,8,Flife. Campbell says losing his dad
OL,9,F"did sort of save me because I had to
OL,10,Fsort myself out".
OL,12,F"My family wouldn't have had it in
OL,13,Fthem to go through it again," he said.
OL,15,FFollowing his time in rehab, Campbell
OL,16,Fsays his family have seen a "massive
OL,17,Fdifference" in him because he is "more
OL,18,Fpresent in their lives".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,369,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1782314307
OL,3,CCampbell Hatton: 'My dad's death saved
OL,4,Cmy life'
OL,6,FNow, with his sights set on returning
OL,7,Fto the boxing ring, he is finally
OL,8,Flooking forward to what lies ahead.
OL,10,F"I'm not just getting by or plodding
OL,11,Fthrough. I'm enjoying my life and seen
OL,12,Fa massive change in the last six
OL,13,Fmonths," Campbell said.
OL,15,F"I'm getting excited by things again
OL,16,Fand looking back with pride because of
OL,17,Fhow far I've come."
OL,19,FCampbell has signed with Misfits
OL,20,FBoxing and will make a huge comeback
OL,21,Fto boxing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
